**Repeated patterns:**
AI infrastructure appears across your three most recent substantial projects (Aether, MindWell, vivaha). You pair this with domain-specific focus—mental health in MindWell, systems architecture in Aether. There's a pattern of building both the platform and the domain application together rather than choosing one or the other.

**Language breadth:**
Rust appears for systems work (Aether). The other projects don't have detected technologies in the evidence, so I can't speak to your full language range.

**Complex systems taken on:**
Aether represents a significant leap in scope and ambition—integrating AI at the OS kernel level is a fundamentally different scale from the developer tooling work. You've also tackled mental health as a domain (MindWell), which adds product and commercial complexity beyond pure infrastructure.

**Confidence: Strong** — derived from stated project purposes and the progression visible in your roadmaps.
